Sorry. That he is at boarding school.

190
00:07:56.018 --> 00:07:57.935
In Svalbard.

191
00:07:57.936 --> 00:07:59.312
That story's holding.

192
00:07:59.313 --> 00:08:01.355
- [chuckles] We're good.
- Mm.

193
00:08:01.356 --> 00:08:03.774
And how-how about you. Sage?

194
00:08:03.775 --> 00:08:05.152
Are you...

195
