228
00:09:27.276 --> 00:09:29.528
You know what's gonna make me happy?

229
00:09:31.071 --> 00:09:33.823
I think I'll be happy when Starlight

230
00:09:33.824 --> 00:09:36.827
and William Butcher are corpses.

231
