234
00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:46.711
we are going to execute
Hugh Campbell. Milk.

235
00:09:46.712 --> 00:09:48.087
and the...

236
00:09:48.088 --> 00:09:49.548
F-French one.

237
00:09:50.549 --> 00:09:53.217
